Define syllable structure
Structure features so that they can be automatically promoted (how?)

Syllable Rule
   Declare phonemes that can appear in syllables
   Start VC end V or sonorant
   <syllables>
      <onsets>
         <onset>
            <require>@s</require>
            <require>@t</require>
            <require>@r</require>
         </onset>
      <initials>
         <initial>
            <require>voicing/voiced manner/vocalic</require>
         </initial>
      </initials>
      <codas>
         <require>voicing
      </codas>
   </syllables>
Morpheme
   List of Morphs
   Morpheme Type

Morph
   Symbol List (Null for Discontinuous)
